                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> Or Click 'Report Now'</h3>
                        <p>Already confident it's a hazard?</p>
                        <p>Tap on the <strong>Report Now</strong> button. You'll be guided to the <strong>AI Analyzer</strong> automatically, where you'll upload the image and then fill out the form to submit your report.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Step 4 -->
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">4</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Submit & Let AI Verify</h3>
